{"id": 2711, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都感受过哪些来自线上社交的压力？", "description": "这么多好友都点赞了，不点赞是不是显得我太高冷了？莫名感受到一点压力。（图片来自：iStock ©️softulka ）", "record_count": 3802, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190103144203auNybzVXWJHT4Dd0.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-04T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 321024, "content": "该不该给老板的微信步数点赞……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223289}, {"id": 321281, "content": "朋友圈内容太少会被别人质疑是小号或者是骗子…无语", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551497}, {"id": 321026, "content": "点赞之交，不点不人道。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078930}, {"id": 323586, "content": "朋友太多，以至于我都不敢发朋友圈！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561580}, {"id": 333059, "content": "🐎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 321029, "content": "好多年龄相近的人有了稳定感情伴侣，而自己还是母胎单身😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 326665, "content": "看不到对方的表情，不能正确判断出对方的情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578458}, {"id": 321034, "content": "永远不让领导看的朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390732}, {"id": 321037, "content": "来至朋友圈的压力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1548841}, {"id": 321038, "content": "发朋友圈要分组发，屏蔽某组或某些人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549067}, {"id": 321040, "content": "群里发红包不抢是不是不太礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490812}, {"id": 321296, "content": "不知道为什么，每次群里聊天我说完就没人接了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551602}, {"id": 321041, "content": "不熟的外地亲戚给我在朋友圈留言 我不是很想回...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1546718}, {"id": 321045, "content": "当你发出一段认为很棒的话，或者重要的话等待回信的时候！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549137}, {"id": 321047, "content": "老板在群里向其他人表扬我，我该怎么回", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549158}, {"id": 321048, "content": "朋友单身，我有娃。朋友老抱怨我没有时间陪她；可是我真的很忙啊，友情的考验", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549166}, {"id": 321049, "content": "尬聊的消息，該怎麼回。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538565}, {"id": 321055, "content": "许久不联系的同学找帮忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549231}, {"id": 321056, "content": "大家都来点赞……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537285}, {"id": 321057, "content": "熟或不熟的朋友让帮忙转发朋友圈宣传她的代购产品/新开小店/网络投票等", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1487251}, {"id": 321060, "content": "打了头几个字后突然不想回了，但是对方显示正在输入", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1547887}, {"id": 321572, "content": "每当我储备的表情包斗不过对面时，就有删人的冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551630}, {"id": 321829, "content": "看了之后有浏览记录", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497432}, {"id": 321062, "content": "稍等等等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 7175}, {"id": 321063, "content": "你蛮热情，对方却只回“哦”，“嗯”，都不知道要聊什么了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1542570}, {"id": 321064, "content": "朋友圈类似的内容，点赞是不是得雨露均沾？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549327}, {"id": 321065, "content": "私人消息发错了群……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549327}, {"id": 321066, "content": "对喜欢的人却不能说  只能像好朋友一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549342}, {"id": 321067, "content": "朋友圈的评论要不要回复不知道回什么回表情会不会不礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187149}, {"id": 321068, "content": "得在有某人的群里面发言或者想发朋友圈，同时不想回某人的信息。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549354}, {"id": 323376, "content": "群里有人发言以后冷场", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502240}, {"id": 321074, "content": "朋友圈总会想去回点什么过去😄", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549472}, {"id": 321075, "content": "最怕在群里刚一说话就冷场的尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549237}, {"id": 321079, "content": "跟不熟的人解释，不知道是不是会解释过头。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540685}, {"id": 320313, "content": "看到“对方正在讲话……”而你正不方便听语音", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 320825, "content": "投票，不匿名那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788683}, {"id": 320314, "content": "有人给你很久之前的状态 or 相册封面点了个赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 308, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 320826, "content": "大家都发红包了，不发是不是不礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 213, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386095}, {"id": 321082, "content": "当交到一个新朋友时，不知道如何把关系维持下去，自己总是不好意思主动去说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1545965}, {"id": 320315, "content": "对方发这个表情到底是个啥意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 317, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 320827, "content": "自己的对象和自己的同性朋友在评论区聊得火热，插话也不是，不插话也不是", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386095}, {"id": 321083, "content": "没有回消息之前是不是不能发动态", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549552}, {"id": 320316, "content": "群里发红包，秒点会不会不太礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 653, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 320828, "content": "在一个人数比较多的群被@到了，又要及时回复，又怕回复得不够得体", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386095}, {"id": 320829, "content": "家庭群里红包第一个抢到就必须说祝福，不知道说什么好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512142}, {"id": 320831, "content": "自己在评论区与别人尬聊，删也不是，不删也不是🌝", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453582}, {"id": 321087, "content": "当别人给我发\"😂\"的时候，是不是代表着我们的对话已经结束了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58857}, {"id": 320832, "content": "过年过节群发的祝福消息，回还是不回？", "image": null, "praise_count": 482, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198394}, {"id": 321089, "content": "老板的长语音", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292442}, {"id": 320834, "content": "上线有提示", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002334}]}